features: Get to know yourself and fill in the“Identity Sculpting”printable template. This includes a bucket list.; Set your goals for the year with the“Annual Goals”printable checklist template. You can add challenges, recipes, travels, and a lot more.; Plan your year ahead based on your defined goals with the"Annual Planner”printable template. You can map out your entire Quarter and Monthly main goals.; Plan your month ahead based on your annual goals with the“Monthly Planner”printable template. Include a new recipe, a new tiny skill, or a new challenge for the month.; Plan your week ahead based on your monthly goals with the“Weekly Planner”printable template. Don’t forget to add all your weekly recurring tasks.; Decide if you want to use the Notion digital version or to print the“63-page eBook”.; Do it all over again during your Annual Review.; Home page with guide; Printable Weekly Planner; Printable Monthly Planner
